text: The Battle of Svolder was the largest naval battle of the Viking age. It was fought on September 9,The Saga of King Olaf Tryggwason, trans. by J. Sephton, London: David Nutt, 1895, p.435. 999 or 1000. == References == Category:Battles of the Middle Ages Category:10th century in Europe Category:999 Category:1000 Category:11th-century conflicts Category:1000s in Europe
